data.description: Don't miss out on this lovely 4 bedroom 2 bathroom modern contemporary brick ranch home in Daytona Beach built in 1992! This spacious and beautifully maintained home has much to offer. Located in a quiet a well maintained neighborhood this home has easy access to I-4, shopping, schools, hospitals and colleges! Zoned for two great Schools: Tomoka Elementary and Spruce Creek High school. This home offers many recent upgrades and features such as: 1 Car Garage, New Garage Door System, Security Alarm System, Gas Water Heater, New Roof 2017, Sprinkler System, Gas Stove, Washer & Dryer, Fenced Back Yard, and Covered Screened Back Porch. This is a great home with many features priced to sell! Come see for yourself. You wont be disappointed. Professional Photos to come.
